#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int t;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
        long long int n;
        scanf("%lld",&n);
        if(n%10==0)
            cout<<n<<endl;
        else
        {
            n=n/10;
            cout<<(n+1)*10<<endl;
        }
    }
    return 0;

}
